# ARCHIVED — Not Deployed

This file is an unreleased concept version of GrokNFT featuring:
- EIP-712 oracle signature scheme for token ID assignment
- Dynamic burn rate per KB of content
- BurnTx pre-registration system
- Capacity-sealed at 6.9 GB

## Why Archived

The team chose the simpler Tier-based variant (no oracle) for the mainnet deployment
because it eliminates the oracle as an attack surface entirely.

## Deployed Contract

The actual deployed GrokNFT contract is at:
`0x5ee102ab33bcc5c49996fb48dea465ec6330e77d`

Source: `contracts/mainnet/GrokNFT.sol`
